  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "J.League Live 64 is a soccer game for the Nintendo 64. It was released only in Japan in 1997. The game has officially licensed players and teams from Japan's J. League. The game was developed by EA and published in the west as Fifa Soccer 64.",
